== 发现 ==

CTCF最早被认为在鸡体内抑制c-myc基因表达。CTCF蛋白和以CCCTC为核心序列的三个规则间隔重复蛋白相结合，故得名CCCTC结合因子<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=A novel sequence-specific DNA binding protein which interacts with three regularly spaced direct repeats of the CCCTC-motif in the 5'-flanking sequence of the chicken c-myc gene|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2284094|last=Lobanenkov|first=V. V.|last2=Nicolas|first2=R. H.|date=1990-12|journal=Oncogene|issue=12|volume=5|pages=1743–1753|issn=0950-9232|pmid=2284094|last3=Adler|first3=V. V.|last4=Paterson|first4=H.|last5=Klenova|first5=E. M.|last6=Polotskaja|first6=A. V.|last7=Goodwin|first7=G. H.|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020154/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2284094|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==功能==
CTCF的主要功能是调控染色质的3D结构<ref name="#1"/>。CTCF和DNA双链结合形成染色质环，并把DNA锚定在细胞结构上（例如核纤层）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Domain organization of human chromosomes revealed by mapping of nuclear lamina interactions|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18463634|last=Guelen|first=Lars|last2=Pagie|first2=Ludo|date=2008-06-12|journal=Nature|issue=7197|doi=10.1038/nature06947|volume=453|pages=948–951|issn=1476-4687|pmid=18463634|last3=Brasset|first3=Emilie|last4=Meuleman|first4=Wouter|last5=Faza|first5=Marius B.|last6=Talhout|first6=Wendy|last7=Eussen|first7=Bert H.|last8=de Klein|first8=Annelies|last9=Wessels|first9=Lodewyk|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002064544/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18463634|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，CTCF还能充当常染色质和异染色质的边界。

DNA的3D结构会影响基因的调控，因此CTCF的活性会影响基因表达。绝缘子能阻碍增强子和启动子的结合，而CTCF是绝缘子的主要活性部分<ref name=":0" />。

== 已观测到的活性 ==

CTCF的结合有多种效应。目前尚不能确定下列功能是直接由CTCF导致。

=== 转录调控 ===
CTCF对于IGF2的抑制起重要作用。具体机制为CTCF和H19基因的基因铭印（ICR）区域、差异甲基化区域-1（DMR-1）和MAR3区域结合<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The many roles of the transcriptional regulator CTCF|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12897849|last=Dunn|first=Katherine L.|last2=Davie|first2=James R.|date=2003-6|journal=Biochemistry and Cell Biology = Biochimie Et Biologie Cellulaire|issue=3|doi=10.1139/o03-052|volume=81|pages=161–167|issn=0829-8211|pmid=12897849|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002064507/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12897849|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 绝缘子 ===
CTCF能通过和目标区域结合以阻碍增强子和启动子的相互作用，从而降低增强子对某些功能域的调控能力<ref>{{Cite journal|title=[Surgical correction of multivalvular defects in patients who had earlier undergone heart surgery]|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2612964|last=Malyshev|first=Iu I.|last2=Iarygin|first2=A. S.|date=1989-11|journal=Grudnaia Khirurgiia (Moscow, Russia)|issue=6|pages=17–20|issn=0017-4866|pmid=2612964|last3=Malyshev|first3=M. Iu|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020200/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2612964|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此之外，CTCF还能作为染色质“路障”，阻止异染色质的进一步形成。

=== 染色质结构调控 ===
CTCF往往以二聚体的形式存在，这会导致DNA形成环状结构。CTCF也经常在DNA和核纤层的结合处出现。使用ChIP-seq技术可以发现CTCF同黏连蛋白一起在基因组内广泛存在，并对染色质的高级结构起调节作用<ref>{{Cite journal|title=CTCF tethers an insulator to subnuclear sites, suggesting shared insulator mechanisms across species|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14759373|last=Yusufzai|first=Timur M.|last2=Tagami|first2=Hideaki|date=2004-01-30|journal=Molecular Cell|issue=2|volume=13|pages=291–298|issn=1097-2765|pmid=14759373|last3=Nakatani|first3=Yoshihiro|last4=Felsenfeld|first4=Gary|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020245/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14759373|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=CTCF-dependent enhancer-blocking by alternative chromatin loop formation|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19074263|last=Hou|first=Chunhui|last2=Zhao|first2=Hui|date=2008-12-23|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|issue=51|doi=10.1073/pnas.0808506106|volume=105|pages=20398–20403|issn=1091-6490|pmc=2629272|pmid=19074263|last3=Tanimoto|first3=Keiji|last4=Dean|first4=Ann|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020316/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19074263|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Electric shocks are ineffective in treatment of lethal effects of rattlesnake envenomation in mice|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3438923|last=Johnson|first=E. K.|last2=Kardong|first2=K. V.|date=1987|journal=Toxicon: Official Journal of the International Society on Toxinology|issue=12|volume=25|pages=1347–1349|issn=0041-0101|pmid=3438923|last3=Mackessy|first3=S. P.|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020351/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3438923|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== RNA剪切调控 ===
CTCF对mRNA剪切有调控作用<ref>{{Cite journal|title=CTCF-promoted RNA polymerase II pausing links DNA methylation to splicing|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21964334|last=Shukla|first=Sanjeev|last2=Kavak|first2=Ersen|date=2011-11-03|journal=Nature|issue=7371|doi=10.1038/nature10442|volume=479|pages=74–79|issn=1476-4687|pmid=21964334|last3=Gregory|first3=Melissa|last4=Imashimizu|first4=Masahiko|last5=Shutinoski|first5=Bojan|last6=Kashlev|first6=Mikhail|last7=Oberdoerffer|first7=Philipp|last8=Sandberg|first8=Rickard|last9=Oberdoerffer|first9=Shalini|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020244/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21964334|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 与DNA结合 ==
CTCF和共有序列CCGCGNGGNGGCAG相结合。这条序列在其结构域中有11个锌指结构。CTCF和基因的结合被CpG的甲基化所影响<ref>{{Cite journal|title=[Nursing--a new future]|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2572726|last=Kroeker|first=L.|date=1989-9|journal=Krankenpflege (Frankfurt Am Main, Germany)|issue=9|volume=43|pages=426–429|issn=0944-9183|pmid=2572726|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020236/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2572726|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Methylation of a CTCF-dependent boundary controls imprinted expression of the Igf2 gene|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10839546|last=Bell|first=A. C.|last2=Felsenfeld|first2=G.|date=2000-05-25|journal=Nature|issue=6785|doi=10.1038/35013100|volume=405|pages=482–485|issn=0028-0836|pmid=10839546|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020211/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10839546|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

CTCF在19个细胞系中大约有55000个共同的DNA结合位点（共77811个独特位点）。CTCF能和不同的锌指结构结合，这让它的功能非常多样化。大约有30000个CTCF的位点功能已经被定义。在人类的不同细胞中大约有15000-40000个CTCF结合位点。除此之外，高分辨率的核小体比对现实CTCF的不同结合位点可能和核小体的定位有关<ref>{{Cite journal|title=[Morphological diagnosis of chronic bronchitis in patients with tuberculosis of the lungs]|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1852749|last=Gomoliako|first=I. V.|date=1991|journal=Problemy Tuberkuleza|issue=4|pages=64–68|issn=0032-9533|pmid=1852749|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020153/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1852749|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=[Severe impalement injury with primary surgical, gynecologic and urologic management]|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2238977|last=Reiher|first=H.|last2=Peschke|first2=G.|date=1990|journal=Zentralblatt Fur Chirurgie|issue=16|volume=115|pages=1041–1043|issn=0044-409X|pmid=2238977|last3=May|first3=G.|last4=Göbel|first4=U.|last5=Randow|first5=H.|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020207/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2238977|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Spontaneous EEG spikes in the normal hippocampus. II. Relations to synchronous burst discharges|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2453330|last=Suzuki|first=S. S.|last2=Smith|first2=G. K.|date=1988-6|journal=Electroencephalography and Clinical Neurophysiology|issue=6|volume=69|pages=532–540|issn=0013-4694|pmid=2453330|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020238/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2453330|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Genome-wide nucleosome positioning during embryonic stem cell development|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23085715|last=Teif|first=Vladimir B.|last2=Vainshtein|first2=Yevhen|date=2012-11|journal=Nature Structural & Molecular Biology|issue=11|doi=10.1038/nsmb.2419|volume=19|pages=1185–1192|issn=1545-9985|pmid=23085715|last3=Caudron-Herger|first3=Maïwen|last4=Mallm|first4=Jan-Philipp|last5=Marth|first5=Caroline|last6=Höfer|first6=Thomas|last7=Rippe|first7=Karsten|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002020304/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23085715|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

